OL,5,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,6,BProgram information:          BPATCH2  
OL,7,                              B(Acorn)  
OL,8,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,9,BTo download programs on a system with  
OL,10,Bthe TFS ROM, run TSOFT and useG*PAGEBto
OL,11,Bselect the page number for the desired 
OL,12,Bfile. e.g.G*PAGE 455                   
OL,14,BFiles can now be downloaded withGLOAD  
OL,15,BorGCHAINBandG*LOADBcommands.           
OL,17,BTo save the file, switch filing system 
OL,18,BwithG*DISCBand eitherGSAVEBfor a BASIC 
OL,19,Bprogram, orG*SAVEBthe downloaded file  
OL,20,Bin memory.                             
OL,22,BSee following pages for save details.  
