OL,5,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,6,BProgram information:         BBUBBLES  
OL,7,                      B(P.Vince/I.Trill)
OL,8,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,9,BA festive program originally broadcast 
OL,10,Bby BBC Telesoftware for Christmas 1985.
OL,12,BThis program has been lightly modified 
OL,13,Bby ZXGuesser to bring seasons greetings
OL,14,Bfrom ChunkyText.                       
OL,20,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,21,BTFS users must use PATCH2 to download  
OL,22,BandGSAVE "BUBBLES"Bor justGRUN         
OL,23,B```````````````````````````````````3/6`
