OL,5,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,6,BProgram information:         BMONITOR  
OL,7,                           B(ZXGuesser) 
OL,8,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,9,BA teletext signal monitor utility for  
OL,10,Bthe Acorn Teletext Adapter.            
OL,12,BDisplays a live view of the packet data
OL,13,Breceived by the adapter.               
OL,15,BThis program does not use any ROM calls
OL,16,Bso is compatible with both TFS and ATS.
OL,18,BDoesAnotBwork in current BeebEm release
OL,19,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,20,BTFS users must use PATCH2 to download. 
OL,21,BSave with:G*SAVE MONITOR 2DC0 2FF7     
OL,22,           G*SAVE MoniTxt 3000 3E3B 0 0 
