OL,5,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,6,BProgram information:         BDATACST  
OL,7,                           B(ZXGuesser) 
OL,8,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,9,BA demonstration datacast reception tool
OL,10,Bwhich displays all messages received on
OL,11,Ba particular datachannel and address.  
OL,13,BMake sure you have selected the channel
OL,14,Bpreset where datacast signals are being
OL,15,Bbroadcast.                             
OL,17,BThis program does not use any ROM calls
OL,18,Bso is compatible with both TFS and ATS.
OL,20,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,21,BTFS users must use PATCH2 to download. 
OL,22,BSave with:G*SAVE DATACST 2400 2A00     
