OL,5,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,6,BText documents:                        
OL,7,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,8,BThe telesofware service can be used to 
OL,9,Bbroadcast text documents, which you can
OL,10,Bdownload to your micro and keep on disc
OL,11,Bfor later reference, or print out.     
OL,13,BThis enables the transmission of much  
OL,14,Blonger articles than would be practical
OL,15,Bto display via rotating subpages on the
OL,16,Bmain ChunkyText service.               
OL,18,BOnce downloaded to your micro, a text  
OL,19,Bfile can be read inGMODE 3Busing a word
OL,20,Bprocessor program or theG*TYPEBcommand.
OL,21,B```````````````````````````````````6/6`
